text: The dotted i (І І̇ і; italics: І І̇ і), also called decimal і (и десятеричное, after its former numeric value), is a letter of the Cyrillic script. == Related letters and other similar characters == * Ι ι : Greek letter Iota * I i : Latin letter I * İ i : Latin letter dotted I * И и : Cyrillic letter I another letter that is romanized as I * Й й : Cyrillic letter Short I Category:Cyrillic letters
title: Dotted I (Cyrillic)
